support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以話啲藍絲俾佢食下煙係好事<br />\n食完分分中叫你打大力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c42c20872e475e7ba7f280179a9ff193aceacbc","tid":1419804,"uid":68541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1bbcc93a1646a760dc1610d7423d21edea66bf","tid":1419804,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27d806266e6a5c0130c2bf13c10fce9f2a37f392","tid":1419804,"uid":20775,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:03:57.000Z","msg":"我老母都係親中藍絲<br />\n琴日天水圍警署 終於俾佢感受到啲煙有幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話放工見天耀好嘈<br />\n諗住經過睇下咩事就俾人射左粒係腳邊<br />\n好彩有人救左佢 幫佢洗眼 佢話估唔到啲狗咁仆街<br />\n仲好佩服啲後生仔頂左咁耐都唔走 仲救左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以話啲藍絲俾佢食下煙係好事<br />\n食完分分中叫你打大力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:35:20.000Z","msg":"我都不停同佢地講<br />\n佢地本身都好禮貌<br />\n你唔去做啲咩 佢地隨時幫返你轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb904737fc1930c80832e44acd9adf768a408f5","tid":1419804,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bdd8776d59906493312d3aa7e61a5b46f619a5","tid":1419804,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"9f803bd56cad67ae1e5633db7ecbe771dc8c89a3","tid":1419804,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:55:39.000Z","msg":"再推"}]}